Operators:-
    Symbol that tell compiler to perform some operations

Tyeps of Operators:

1. Arithmatic Operators:
 a. Binary Operators:-
    +, -, *, /, %.
 
 b. Unary Operators:
    ++, --

2. Increment Operators:-
 a. Pre increment:-
    ++a 

 b. Post increment:-
    a++ 

 c. Post decrement:-
    a--

 d. Pre decrement:-
    --a 
